<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f4f4f4;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#171717;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#f4f4f4;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding:20px;">
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#ffffff;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:20px;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;color:#16d995;">
              Nachricht erfolgreich erhalten | Message Received Successfully 📬
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:0 20px 16px 20px;font-size:20px;">
              Vielen Dank für deine Kontaktaufnahme. Ich habe deine Nachricht erhalten und werde mich so bald wie möglich bei dir melden.<br><br>Mit freundlichen Grüßen,<br>Marcel Arndt
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:0 20px 16px 20px;font-size:20px;">
              Thank you for contacting me. I have received your message and will get back to you as soon as possible.<br><br>Best regards,<br>Marcel Arndt
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:64px 20px 8px 20px;font-size:20px;">
              Deine Nachricht | Your message:
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:0 20px 20px 20px;">
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:24px 12px;background-color:#e5e5e5;color:#414141;font-size:16px;white-space:pre-wrap;">
                    Subject: {{subject}}
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:24px 12px;background-color:#e5e5e5;color:#414141;font-size:16px;white-space:pre-wrap;">
                    Message: {{message}}
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
